## 1. What’s New

### 1.1 Feature Summary

**Kiro SDLC Agents** is a new VS Code / Kiro IDE extension that brings a multi-agent SDLC pipeline directly into your workspace. With a single command, you can inject AI agent configurations for Business Analysis, Solution Architecture, QA, Development, DevOps, UI, and Security — enabling structured, AI-assisted software development workflows.

This initial release (v1.0.0) delivers the **Extension Core** — the foundation that activates the extension, registers commands, and provides visual status feedback.

### 1.2 User-Facing Changes

| # | Change | Description | Impact |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Extension auto-activates on startup | Extension is always ready | Low |
| 2 | 5 commands in Command Palette | Inject All, Inject Selective, Run Indexer, Update, Show Status | High |
| 3 | Status bar indicator | Shows SDLC health at a glance | Medium |
| 4 | Confirmation dialogs | Prevents accidental file overwrites | Medium |
| 5 | Code Intelligence Indexer | Auto-detects runtime and indexes codebase | High |

## 2. Technical Changes

### 2.1 API Changes (VS Code Commands)

| Type | Command ID | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| New | kiroSdlc.injectAll | Injects all SDLC components into workspace |
| New | kiroSdlc.injectSelective | Multi-select component injection |
| New | kiroSdlc.runIndex | Executes code intelligence indexer |
| New | kiroSdlc.update | Updates agents (overwrites existing) |
| New | kiroSdlc.status | Shows component presence status |

### 2.2 Database Changes

**Not Applicable.** Client-side extension with no database.

### 2.3 Configuration Changes

| Property | Change Type | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| kiroSdlc.autoIndex | New | Auto-run indexer after injection (default: true) |
| kiroSdlc.preferredIndexer | New | Preferred indexer runtime (default: “auto”) |

### 2.4 Infrastructure Changes

| Component | Change | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| GitHub Actions CI | New | Build verification on push/PR |
| GitHub Actions Publish | New | Automated Marketplace publish on tag |
| VS Code Marketplace | New | Extension listing |
| Open VSX Registry | New | Extension listing for Kiro IDE |

## 3. Bug Fixes

No bug fixes included in this release. This is the initial release (v1.0.0).

## 4. Known Issues & Limitations

| # | Issue | Impact | Workaround | Target Fix |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | Publisher ID is placeholder | Cannot publish until changed | Update package.json | KSA-11 |
| 2 | Repository URL is placeholder | Wrong link on Marketplace | Update package.json | KSA-11 |
| 3 | Only first workspace folder used | Multi-root limited | Open target as primary | Future |
| 4 | Status bar doesn’t auto-refresh | May be stale | Run Show Status | Future |
| 5 | Indexer timeout fixed at 120s | Large codebases may timeout | Manual run | Future |

